                            <comment id="60957" author="adilger" created="Fri, 21 Jun 2013 01:02:36 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Since 2.4.0 was shipped without this change, and we are instead pursuing a path to patch the quota code to fix the locking bottlenecks, I&apos;m closing this bug as &quot;Won&apos;t Fix&quot;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="59337" author="adilger" created="Mon, 27 May 2013 02:38:33 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;No, tune2fs is only for ldiskfs.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="59331" author="bzzz" created="Sun, 26 May 2013 17:15:02 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Andreas, are you suggesting to disable accounting by default in ZFS as well?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
